<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Google platforms including Gmail and YouTube temporarily went down across the United States on Thursday evening, sparking tens of thousands of complaints. </p>

<p>According to online monitor DownDetector, Google services crashed in many parts of the country at 9pm Eastern Time. </p>

<p>An outage map shows the east and west coasts were most severely affected, but there were also problems in parts of the south and Midwest. </p>

<p>Problems were reported to be resolved by 9.23pm.  </p>

<p>Google platforms including Gmail and YouTube temporarily went down across the United States on Thursday evening, sparking tens of thousands of complaints.</p>
